WEBVTT

00:02.785 --> 00:04.885
Sure, it's nice to pretend you're royal for the day.

00:05.092 --> 00:06.371
Have a cup of tea with the Queen.

00:07.236 --> 00:09.839
It's something that not a lot of people have done.

00:09.943 --> 00:12.907
It's only available two months out of the year.

00:13.012 --> 00:15.575
For summertime, this is one place that they should,...

00:15.985 --> 00:17.777
...the Buckingham Palace, that they should visit.

00:18.099 --> 00:20.990
I never thought I'd get the chance to see it from the inside.

00:21.175 --> 00:21.963
It's wonderful.

00:25.750 --> 00:27.309
Take time and enjoy.

00:27.837 --> 00:29.608
Come in August and September when it's open,...

00:29.674 --> 00:31.821
...otherwise you won't get a chance to see it.

